Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:20.91,Title Part 4,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(648,643)\pos(143,900)\fs60}Episode 21: {\fs80} Kira Yoshikage Wants a Quiet Life Part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:19.57,Main,Lady,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mr. Kira? Umm, Mr. Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:29.37,Main,Lady,0,0,0,,Mr. Kira, if you aren't busy, \Nwould you like to have lunch with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.38,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'll have to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:37.76,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I need to go deliver these documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:38.84,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:42.97,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Give up on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:46.22,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,He never feels like socializing with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:50.52,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Whenever we have him with us during group outings, I can never tell if he's enjoying it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:54.73,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Kira Yoshikage, age thirty-three, single.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:59.36,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Even though he's dedicated to his work \Nand gets it done efficiently, he has absolutely no passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:05.20,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's a decent guy, but he's really plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:14.67,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Now, now, what have I done to upset you this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:19.30,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,The new women at work simply\N invited me out for lunch, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:22.55,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I already promised that\N I would be having lunch with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:25.72,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...and I'm very much a man of my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.06,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You heard me decline them immediately, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:34.11,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Have I ever left you by yourself? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:40.82,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Anyway, you shouldn't concern yourself with it, so let's just pick out our sandwiches and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:43.07,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Here. Which one would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.24,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Doesn't the bread feel incredibly moist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:52.04,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,This place is popular for its sandwiches\N since they're made with bread freshly baked at 11:00 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:54.88,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,By 1:00 PM, they're usually completely sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:58.34,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You can feel their warmth right through the wrapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:02.63,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,The cutlets they use in their sandwiches \Nare crispy and freshly fried, too. {the originally wording made it sound like "freshly crispy" which seemed weird.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:05.80,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Oh no... {For BDs: Consider changing to "Oh no..." for reasons we talked about}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:09.72,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You pierced the wrapper, \Nand now all the sauce is spilling out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.39,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You naughty girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:33.79,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Well... Since this one has a hole in it, \Nlet's buy the one below instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.29,Main,Dude,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:54.31,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Morioh is such a beautiful town!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:58.31,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Could there possibly be another town as beautiful as ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:01.57,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It feels like we're having a picnic. {chew}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.50,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,She's beginning to smell foul...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:19.79,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,I suppose it's about time the two of us broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.71,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,I'll sever all ties.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.13,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,"Sever" all ties...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:29.93,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Perhaps I'll find a new girl vacationing here or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:39.23,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:05:59.58,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.88,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Shigechi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:03.80,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Guh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:06.42,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Mr. Josuke, Mr. Okuyasu! {The "Mr." is here because of the ending of Shigechi's Harvest Part 2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:10.30,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Yo! You're just the guy we were lookin' for, Shigechi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:13.93,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,This is kinda short notice, \Nbut could you lend us some lunch money?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:16.10,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,We forgot to bring money today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.69,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Huh? Whatcha talkin' 'bout?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:22.19,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,You fellers gots all dat money from da lottery!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:24.98,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,We put it all in savings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:30.53,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,It's a big pain in the ass goin' to the bank for a little lunch money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:32.78,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,All we need's a thousand yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.29,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:35.66,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,C'mon, can'tcha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:38.41,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,We'll go to the bank right after school!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:42.42,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,That bag! You got a sandwich at St. Gentlemen, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.59,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You got there before they sold out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:48.38,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Dis's all mine! Y'all ain't gettin' nuthin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:51.59,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Guess I gots no choice... I'll gives y'all da money...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.35,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.85,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:07:02.27,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I'm gunna puts a lil' note in my planner, \Nso y'all better pays me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:05.11,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,You're the one who never pays {\i1}us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:08.82,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Lesse... "June 24th."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:08.82,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,{\an8}Anyway, thanks again for helping us out, Shigechi! {I'm pretty sure Shigechi never helped them out before, so it should be thanks again for helping instead of thanks for helping again?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:12.03,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,"Lended 1,000 yen"... Lended?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:10.70,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,{\an8}See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:15.53,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Umm, how's dat kanji for {\i1}lended{\i0} go again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:16.62,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Lended...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.45,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Oh wells!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:20.46,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I jus' gots t'write it in hiragana!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:24.34,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I dunno how t'write Josuke an' Okuyasu in kanji, anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:25.80,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.67,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,M-My sandwich!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.80,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Wh-Where'd it go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:38.35,Thoughts,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah, it's right dere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:42.10,Thoughts,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I dunno how it gots dere, but oh wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:52.78,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:57.54,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Josuke, Mr. Okuyasu, waits fer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:08:01.54,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Y'all still gots t'put your thumbprints in my planner! \NYour thumbprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:08.30,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Did that really just happen? You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:10.76,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Did he take my bag after mistaking it for his own?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:13.43,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Man, what a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.26,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,How can we even do that right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:18.47,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,That's easy! Ya just gotta cut your thumb with a knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:21.02,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I-It don't gots t'be like dat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:23.77,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Well, jus' signs it fer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:27.77,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Hey, let's get a move on to St. Gentlemen!\N They're gonna sell out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:31.28,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,This is bad... If he opens that bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:35.16,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,She's wearing the ring I bought for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.99,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,And she's covered in my fingerprints...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:42.71,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Once the police get involved, it will only be\N a matter of time before they trace the ring back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:52.47,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,I, Kira Yoshikage, haven't left behind \Na single piece of evidence in fifteen years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:54.97,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,I'm not about to let some brat ruin everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.18,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Josuke, we gotta hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:58.72,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:01.22,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I'll waits fer y'all outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.23,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.60,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,I need to take it from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:09.23,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,My best course of action is to\N take it while he isn't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.74,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Shigechi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:18.20,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,You're one lucky son of a bitch, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:22.83,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,St. Gentlemen is already sold out of \Nsandwiches for the day! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:26.25,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Oh, really?! Dey's all solds out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:28.67,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Ain't dat a shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:33.51,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,If ya likes, I'll gives ya mine fer jus' ten thousand yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:38.72,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,You're such a fuckin' cheapskate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:42.01,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Guess we ain't got no choice. Let's go to Hokaben, Josuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.60,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Hokaben, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:48.23,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,We won't be able to get enough food with a drink if we only spend five hundred yen each.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:51.44,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Should be enough if we just get \Nour regular school lunch, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:54.15,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Koichi said he was getting school lunch, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:57.78,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,No way! He's with Yamagishi Yukako, ain't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:01.70,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Ya expect me t'eat lunch with those two lovebirds?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:07.12,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,An' anyway, the school lunch meat's just a milimeter thick...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:10.04,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,...an' do ya got any idea what\N that shit in the miso soup really is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:15.51,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Y'know, dey gots lotsa drinks in \Nda prep room at my school's gym!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:19.93,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Da gym teacher's always in dere \Nsneakin' coffee an' tea an' stuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:27.69,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,'Cause all da teachers're in da break room fer lunch, \NI sometimes gets t'sneaks in the window and gets some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:30.77,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Wanna gets yer lunch an' go with me t'school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:34.65,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,What the hell, man? Are you stealing from your school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.61,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,You're a total cheapskate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:41.03,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Least we can do is buy our own drinks! \NWe ain't that greedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:42.28,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:46.04,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Gah, I was jus' tryin' t'be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:51.04,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Bye-bye! Oh, an' ya better be payin' me backs tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:04.76,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Oh, 'scuse me, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:07.73,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I should be watchin' wheres I'm goin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:08.98,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:11.77,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:15.23,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,It's good that he separated from his friends, \Nbut he's going back to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:18.11,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,He must be waiting to eat there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:19.61,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:23.41,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,They called him Shigechi, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:27.62,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,He'll definitely open the bag within the next few minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:31.33,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,This is very bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:51.35,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Finally, I gets t'eats my lunch in peace an' quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:02.57,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Whoopsie! Almost forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:06.08,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I gots t'brew my coffee b'fore I eats my sandwiches!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:10.45,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Always gots t'have my coffee b'fore I leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:18.21,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,You're very fortunate, Shigechi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:22.63,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I would have eliminated you if you had caught \Nso much as a glimpse of the contents of that bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:31.18,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Hey, Josuke! This's the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.48,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Not as big as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:35.48,Secondary,Kira,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:38.90,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,They said they weren't coming here earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:43.74,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Shigechi, you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:45.20,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Shigechi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:49.74,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Oh, heya! If it ain't Mr. Okuyasu an' Mr. Josuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:53.62,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,We thought about it, \Nand we decided we could go for some free coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:57.50,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,We got ourselves a five hundred yen \Nrice, fish, meat, and veggies lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:13:03.22,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Hmph! An' y'all were callin' me a dirty ol' thief...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:05.26,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Y'all gots some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:08.05,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,C'mon, you don't need to be like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:11.68,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Sometimes people change their mind after a little while!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:15.44,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:20.15,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Eliminating one of them would be simple, \Nbut all three at once is too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:24.65,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Damn! She's only a few centimeters away...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:31.45,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Shigechi, get me a drink, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:33.79,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I'll have Japanese tea instead of coffee, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.96,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,There any black tea? Like milk tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:40.34,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Yucky! Yer gunna eat dat stuff with milk tea? Dat's nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:44.59,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Damn! He's going to eat his lunch up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:48.84,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,At this rate, he's going to open the bag right in front of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:00.11,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Aww, soy sauce again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:03.03,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,These cutlets always come with soy sauce...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:05.40,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Huh? Cutlets are supposed to be eaten with soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:07.28,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Huh?! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.03,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,They're supposed to be eaten with cutlet sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:12.49,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Ya gotta use cutlet sauce since it's got the same name!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:13.87,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.88,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,I have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.22,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:35.02,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:36.43,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:42.56,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:49.78,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:51.20,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:04.42,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Hey! What're ya doin', Mr. Josuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:09.38,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Ya wasn't tryin' t'steal my sandwich, was ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:12.22,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Of course not! Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:16.68,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,I heard a weird noise near your bag, \Nso I went to take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.56,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Don'tcha dare ever touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:21.15,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,No way ya'd jus' be lookin' at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:28.53,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,"Dat dere teriyaki chicken sandwich is my favoritest one, Shigechi! \NGimme a bite!" is whatcha was thinkin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:31.49,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You sure are a selfish little guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.53,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,You got my tea yet? Where's my tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:35.03,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Don't forget my milk tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:37.12,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I was jus' about t'make 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:43.25,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.43,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.55,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I gots yer tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:57.18,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I gots the Japanese tea an' da milk tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:57.97,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.56,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.48,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:06.65,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Wh-Where d-didja puts my sandwich?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:08.44,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:10.24,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Looks like it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:13.49,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,But we don't know where it went. Right, Okuyasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:14.32,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.95,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Quit messin' around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:19.45,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,How couldja not know?! Y'all're da only ones here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.75,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Seriously, we have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:24.33,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Yeah, we ain't messin' with ya or nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.84,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,No joke, we really ain't got a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:31.09,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Y-You jerks! I'm abouts t'get real mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:32.63,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,We're telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:35.09,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,You really gotta cut this shit out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.14,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Why would we take your sand{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:40.43,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I'll know if y'all're lyin' soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:43.89,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I jus' gots t'get Harvest t'look through da room!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:46.98,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,You're a real fuckin' pain! Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:50.48,Main,Okuyasu,0,0,0,,Look around as much as ya want!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:53.40,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,We have no reason to steal your sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:05.83,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,What's going on? \NI can't see what they're doing from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:10.21,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,What is that brat up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.34,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.88,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,I can hear you in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.13,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Dat's da gym teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:18.72,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,Damn! We need to get out of here, Shigechi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:21.35,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,B-But my sandwich!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.43,Main,Josuke,0,0,0,,We don't have time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:26.40,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:32.03,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Damn, I can't believe those kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:38.70,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,I knew something was up when my coffee and tea \Nkept disappearing so quickly. No wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:43.00,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,I need to lock this place up more carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.47,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,It was a bit messy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:02.39,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,...I managed to overcome that difficult situation and successfully retrieve her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:10.65,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,I, Kira Yoshikage, have always felt\N the guiding hand of lady luck protect me wherever I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:16.53,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,As long as my actions are carefully planned and carried out without hesitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:20.37,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,...I truly believe I can live \Nthe rest of my life out in happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.49,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,What a close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:27.54,Thoughts,Kira,0,0,0,,I'm so happy that you've returned to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.29,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:38.13,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,What da heck's a feller like you doin' with my sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:44.14,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,An' what're ya doin' bein' all sneaky \Naround my middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:49.52,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Would you happen to be talking to me, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:52.40,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I haven't a clue what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:54.48,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,This is my sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:56.78,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I bought it at St. Gentlemen earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:59.95,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh! Dat bag's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:02.62,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,I gots proof dat it's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:05.49,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,You jus' ain't smart enough t'gets it! {not smart enough? What does being smart have to do with it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:08.50,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Gets it back fer me, Harvest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:14.92,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Wh-What? What's going on? \NThe bag is being pulled...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:26.56,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Wh-Wha... Wh-Wha... My sandwich...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:31.90,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Is... Is dat somebody's hand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:37.03,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,What have you done? Now you've seen her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:38.78,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,And what's more, brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:43.41,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...you seem to have the same kind of power that I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:46.16,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Ya can sees my Harvest?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:49.41,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Tell me, what's dis hand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:53.13,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Why's ya walkin' around with a hand in yer bag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:56.92,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Are you by yourself? Those two friends of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:59.80,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I believe you called them Josuke and Okuyasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:03.43,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Do they also have powers like yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:05.68,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:09.31,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Move even a little an' I'll attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:15.90,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Yer a real creepy feller! Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:19.19,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Yer givin' me da heebie jeebies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:23.32,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Don't move! Don't move at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:29.58,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,My name is Kira Yoshikage. I'm thirty-three years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:35.13,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,My house is a villa located at the northeastern point of Morioh\N with all the others, and I'm unmarried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:44.38,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I work for the chain store Kame Yu, \Nand I'm always home by eight o'clock at the latest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:49.76,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I don't smoke, but I do occasionally drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:55.48,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'm in bed by eleven o'clock to ensure that \NI get a full eight hours of sleep, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:21:03.57,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Before going to sleep, I always drink a warm glass of milk \Nand do my twenty minutes of stretches...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:05.99,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...so that I can sleep soundly until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:12.87,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Like an infant, I wake up feeling \Nno fatigue or stress in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:15.96,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,My doctor told me I had no health issues \Nduring my latest checkup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:19.42,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,Wh-What're ya sayin' t'me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:26.26,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I'm trying to explain to you how I live my quiet life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:30.56,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I take care to avoid troubling things,\N such as making enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:34.02,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...winning or losing, and anything else \Nthat could cause me restless sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:37.77,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,It's the only way I've found to cope with society.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:42.07,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,I've gone to great lengths to ensure my continued happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:48.99,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,However, if the need to fight arises, I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:58.25,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Simply put, Shigechi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:22:01.80,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...you are a nuisance that will hinder my sleep if left unchecked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:03.76,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,That makes you my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:08.64,Main,Shigechi,0,0,0,,D-Dat's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.64,0:22:14.52,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Killer Queen! This is the name I've chosen for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:20.77,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,Before you can speak another word, \NI'm going to completely eliminate you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:24.57,Main,Kira,0,0,0,,...so that my sleep will go undisturbed tonight.
