Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.27,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HFAF2ED&}Something important is being taken from me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:26.69,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HFAF2ED&}By a demon that's thrust itself into my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:30.06,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HC4B3D4&}Everything is crumbling around me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:32.86,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HECEEEE&}Living my life as if everything was fine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:35.24,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HECEEEE&}Until suddenly it was stolen away without warning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:38.70,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HECEEEE&}This is my only chance to take it back
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:43.04,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HF8E3D2&}Those who fight with a heart pierced by the arrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:46.54,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HF8E3D2&}Are a beautiful sight to behold
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:47.58,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)}{\1c&HF8E3D2&}Anywhere you go I'll chase you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:49.21,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}{\1c&HC3F0FA&}Anywhere you go I'll chase you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:51.34,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HC3F0FA&}I'll always chase you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:53.50,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HC3F0FA&}I will chase you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:55.09,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HD6ECF9&}You can't escape me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.76,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HD6ECF9&}Run faster as I chase you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:01:59.89,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HD6ECF9&}Even tomorrow I'll chase you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:02.76,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&HD6ECF9&}Until I finally pummel you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:08.39,Part 4 OP2 English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\1c&&HEEF7F1&&}My perseverance will propel me forward to achieve victory
